title: TestCompoundSetfieldPanel

\whitespace trim

! Compound +fields setfield live test

Target: [[TestCompoundSetfield]]

!! 1. Raw `text` field (the compound source)

<pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:.85em">
<$view tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" field="text"/>
</pre>

!! 2. Derived fields on the tiddler

<table class="tc-view-field-table">
<tbody>
<$list filter="[[TestCompoundSetfield]fields[]sort[title]] -text -type -tags -created -modified" variable="fieldName">
<tr><td><code><<fieldName>></code></td><td>{{{ [[TestCompoundSetfield]get<fieldName>] }}}</td></tr>
</$list>
</tbody>
</table>

!! 3. Sub-entry `type:` metadata (via compound-field-type)

* email type → <code>{{{ [[TestCompoundSetfield]compound-field-type[email]] }}}</code>
* nickname type → <code>{{{ [[TestCompoundSetfield]compound-field-type[nickname]] }}}</code> ''(should be empty)''
* body type → <code>{{{ [[TestCompoundSetfield]compound-field-type[body]] }}}</code>

!! 4. Tests — click each, then look back at sections 1–3

<$button> a) Update plain field (nickname → "NewNick")
<$action-setfield $tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" $index="nickname" $value="NewNick"/>
</$button>

<$button> b) Update metadata field (email → "fresh@example.com"; `type: email` MUST stay)
<$action-setfield $tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" $index="email" $value="fresh@example.com"/>
</$button>

<$button> c) Add new field (city = "Vienna")
<$action-setfield $tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" $index="city" $value="Vienna"/>
</$button>

<$button> d1) Delete sub-entry via `$action-setfield $index=nickname` (no `$value`)
<$action-setfield $tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" $index="nickname"/>
</$button>

<$button> d2) Delete derived field via `$action-deletefield nickname`
<$action-deletefield $tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" nickname/>
</$button>

<$button> e) Set metadata via `$indexProperty` (type=date-time on email)
<$action-setfield $tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" $index="email" $indexProperty="type" $value="date-time"/>
</$button>

<$button> f) Remove metadata via `$indexProperty` (drop type from email; unwraps to plain string)
<$action-setfield $tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" $index="email" $indexProperty="type"/>
</$button>

<$button>
<$action-setfield $tiddler="TestCompoundSetfield" $field="text" $value={{{ [[TestCompoundSetfield_initial]get[text]] }}}/>
Reset compound text to initial (leaves stale derived fields — diagnostic)
</$button>
